Title: An Act Changing the Name of the Atok Elementary School, Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, to Filomena P. Cating Elementary School
Data:
BATAS PAMBANSA Blg. 857
An Act Changing the Name of the Atok Elementary School, Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, to Filomena P. Cating Elementary School
Section 1. The name of the Atok Elementary School, in the Municipality of Atok, Province of Benguet, is changed to Filomena P. Cating Elementary School.
Section 2. This Act shall take effect upon its approval.1Ã¢wphi1
Approved: April 27, 1984
